thread.title: Derek Diener

author: Derek Diener
title: Derek Diener
text: We had a normal experience. Found tickets via another site, they were there as advertised (which isn't always the case with other sellers). Paid for tickets, received them and clear instructions/ communications from Supersavertravel. There was nothing out of the ordinary in my trip that allow me to actually critique anything other than this normal purchase and communication. Satisfied.
